---
import Project1 from '../assets/project_1.jpeg';
---

<div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-900 py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
      My Projects
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-4">
      Here are some of the projects I have worked on.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-8">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 shadow-md rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
      >
        <img
          src={Project1.src}
          alt="Project 1"
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="p-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
            Content Management System
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">
            As part of the Software Engineering 2 course, I led the development of a modular and efficient Content Management System (CMS). This project enhanced my skills in team management, allowing me to coordinate efforts among team members effectively. I also mastered modular structuring, ensuring the system's components were scalable and maintainable, and focused on task distribution to streamline development and meet deadlines efficiently. The CMS provided practical experience in balancing technical implementation with collaborative teamwork.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/frandepy2/CMS-IS2"
            target="_blank"
            class="mt-4 inline-block text-blue-500 hover:underline"
          >
            See in GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Añadir más proyectos aquí -->

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
